name: Ghost Train
description: The second mint from my Wabi-Sabi Collection. A mother and child walk down a train platform in South Korea. The black and white, as well as the imperfections because of the malfunctioning camera gave this photo a spooky vibe. It's almost as if I captured and image from the other side, a spirits from the past. This picture was taken with a Zenit TTL and Kodak Tri-X 400.
